    "Besides, some of the customized words removed, which are the high frequent verbs in the novel such as \"said\", \"feel\", \"know\", \"come\" and the name of the characters.",
    "Lemmatization.",
    "This technique removes the affixes of words that are in its dictionary.",
    "Lemmatization results in a list of root words (lemmas) to remove redundant words in text.",
    "For example, lemmatize 'plays' to 'play'."
